        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1259",
        "content": "The plate and the more valuable pictures found a safer home in London, but the bulk of the things went country ways, and were entrusted to the guardianship of Miss Avery.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
